程序包 cn.ficos.Compiler.Exceptions

  • 异常错误概要 
    异常错误 说明
    ParaMismatch
    This exception indicates that function's AVT does not match its FNT.
    Redefine
    The "redefine" fault.
    Undefined
    The "undefine" fault
  • 错误概要 
    错误 说明
    Bug_FuncNotDefine
    This error is intended to indicate there exists a bug in defining function in Field_FunctionCollector
    Bug_New_a_BuiltIn_Type
    This class is intended to indicate there is a bug in trying to new a built-in type in the heap
    Bug_SymbolTableInitializationFault
    This exception indicates there are problems when initializing the SymbolTable
    Bug_TextError
    The error will be throw when AST come across an unexpected text
    Bug_WrongReturn
    This exception indicated that there exists a wrong return when building AST
    FalseArrayInit
    This exception indicates that the an array type's base type is initialized by "null". see ArrayType
    SemanticError
    This exception indicates that there exists semantic errors in the source code.
